column5: My buddy's (and board member) new PB Walleye he caught today on Quinte. Measured a solid 31.5" x 18.5" and weighed in at 12.52 lbs!  Got to test out in the new Hero 3 camera, and boy it is sweet! Awesome to have on the boat.  Video
beatuy fish. so jealous!   whats up with the video quality? usually go pro vids are flawless HD
Awesome fish and video!!!     My guess is when it was compressed to upload to youtube it lost it's HD properties.  Can happen if you choose a file format that compresses it too much.
Yup! I was filming in 1440p, so it must have compressed it quite a bit.
sweet walleye! congrats to your buddy!
